9.0.1 Hello world
-----------------

As a first example, we will take a sodium atom.  With your favourite
text editor, create the following input "inp".
       SystemName = 'Na'
       CalculationMode = 1
       %Species
         'Na' | 22.989768 | 11 | "tm2" | 0 | 0
       %
       %Coordinates
         'Na' | 0.0 | 0.0 | 0.0 | no
       %
       Radius = 12.0
       Spacing = .6
       TypeOfMixing = 2

